[111.745715, "o", "\u001b[01m\u001b[Kdrive_h/run.c:\u001b[m\u001b[K In function ‘\u001b[01m\u001b[Krun_case\u001b[m\u001b[K’:\r\n\u001b[01m\u001b[Kdrive_h/run.c:11:5:\u001b[m\u001b[K \u001b[01;35m\u001b[Kwarning: \u001b[m\u001b[K‘\u001b[01m\u001b[Kstrncpy\u001b[m\u001b[K’ output may be truncated copying 31 bytes from a string of length 31 [\u001b[01;35m\u001b[K\u001b]8;;https://gcc.gnu.org/onlinedocs/gcc-14.2.0/gcc/Warning-Options.html#index-Wno-stringop-truncation\u0007-Wstringop-truncation\u001b]8;;\u0007\u001b[m\u001b[K]\r\n   11 |     \u001b[01;35m\u001b[Kstrncpy(res->name, plan->name, sizeof(res->name) - 1)\u001b[m\u001b[K;"]
